<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink365">
<l>kaṇamā tolaiccit taṉṉaiyar tanta</l>
<l>niṇavūṉ valcip paṭupuḷ ḷōppu</l>
<l>nalamā ṇeyiṟṟi pōlap palamiku</l>
<l>naṉṉala nayavara vuṭaiyai</l>
<l>yeṉṉōṟ ṟaṉaiyō māviṉ ṟaḷirē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>You have desire for [obtaining] many great traits  </l>
<l>like [those of] a glorious eyiṉar girl who chases birds  </l>
<l>that flock on food of fatty meat, brought by her kin </l>
<l>after they felled a deer from the herd. </l>
<l>But what penance did you do [for this]? O tender mango sprout! </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
